high_descs: Move forward, then turn left at the kitchen island, then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the stove.
Turn around, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and return to the stove.
Put the kettle on the stove, on the back right range.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle on the stove.

high_descs: Pick up the kettle off of the front right burner of the stove.
Walk over to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the kettle into the sink basin and turn on the faucet, after a couple seconds turn the faucet off and remove the kettle from the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the stove.
Put the clean kettle on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle on the stove.

high_descs: Walk to the stove ahead of you.
Pick up a pot from the stove.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Place the pot in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Walk back to the stove on your left.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Wash a pot and replace it.
